<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="SB0209" sponsor="Derrin R. Owens" designation="SB" otherSponsor="" otherHouse="House" subNumber="02" subSponsor="Derrin R. Owens" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0907" date="2/7/2026 22:02:510" printDate="02-07 22:56" subVer="2" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>3</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="05/06/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="1" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" sort="79 04 06090020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">79-4-609</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="2" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>4</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Gooseberry Narrows State Park Study</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Derrin R. Owens</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>House Sponsor: </otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill addresses a study for the creation of Gooseberry Narrows State Park.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">defines the gooseberry narrows; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">requires the Division of State Parks to:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10" level="2"><marker pairid="0"/><marker pairid="1"/><marker pairid="2"/><marker pairid="3"/>study the feasibility and cost of developing and constructing a state park and dam in <ln numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11"/>the gooseberry narrows; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12" level="2">recommend funding from the Legislature for the creation of the Gooseberry Narrows <ln numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13"/>State Park.</hl></hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="15">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="17">None</ocNone><sa numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saent numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="79-4-609" src="code" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" buid="1" sort="79 04 06090020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="0-20"><bold>79-4-609</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="21"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="0-22">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="1" num="79-4-609" type="enact" src="code" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" sort="79 04 06090020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-2" number="79-4-609" type="enact"><secline lineno="23">Section 1. Section <bold>79-4-609</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="24"><bold>79-4-609<parens/>. Gooseberry Narrows State Park -- Study -- Report.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="1-1" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="11" groupid="8" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section, "gooseberry narrows" means the land on Gooseberry Creek <ln numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-4"/>between the Lower Gooseberry Dam and Fairview Lakes described by the map and legal <ln numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-5"/>description on file with the division.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-35" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-6" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" space="false"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><subsection ssid="1-38" dnum="_-o:a-i" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2" placement="sameline"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="166" groupid="114" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The division shall study the feasibility of creating the Gooseberry Narrows State <ln numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-7"/>Park, including:</amend><subsection ssid="1-43" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-8" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3" tab="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="211" groupid="146" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">any necessary requirement for the development or construction of a dam and <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-9"/>reservoir at Gooseberry Narrows State Park;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-36" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3" tab="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="179" groupid="125" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the expected cost to the state of:</amend><subsection ssid="1-44" dnum="_-o:A-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-11" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="4"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(A)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="214" groupid="148" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">transferring, exchanging, or purchasing all federally managed lands in the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-12"/>gooseberry narrows;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-37" dnum="_-o:B-i" numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="4"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(B)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="203" groupid="141" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">constructing and developing infrastructure needed for the state park; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-40" dnum="_-o:C-i" numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-14" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="4"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(C)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="210" groupid="145" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">constructing and developing a dam and reservoir in the gooseberry narrows; <ln numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-15"/>and</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-46" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-16" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3" tab="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="221" groupid="153" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a recommendation for the Legislature to appropriate funds for the creation of the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-17"/>Gooseberry Narrows State Park.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-39" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-18" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1009" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="190" groupid="133" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">Before November 30, 2026, the division shall report the results of the study <ln numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-19"/>described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="79-4-609(2)(a)">(2)(a)</xref> to the Natural Resources, Agriculture, and <ln numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="1-20"/>Environment Interim Committee.</amend></subsection></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="2" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="43" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="43">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="44"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="5/6/2026">May 6, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>2-7-26 10:56 PM</tm></rev></foot></leg>